Examples of using quire.tex

If this is used, margin size changes when number of pages changes, which means text may
fall-off from printable area;
if we keep margin size fixed, \hsize changes when number of pages changes, which influences
line and page breaking of all document.
If document is finished, \shthickness may be used, but side lines to cut protruding pages
can't be printed because they are too close to sheet border, outside of printable area;
if you use this case, temorarily comment \errmessage line above.
\shthickness is not needed at all if we cut each sheet into 2 halves and use binding or
wire spiral, instead of just folding each sheet and using staples.

Значение \shthickness в документе не должно быть 0pt (по умоланию 0.2mm) только
когда
изменение \hsize не влияет на количество страниц (например, стихи.tex).
В остальных случаях значение должно быть 0pt (например, иллюзии.tex).
